Description:
    Creates a new basic front-end web application for banners.

Options:
    

Example:
    yo banner

    This will create:
        Gruntfile.js: Configuration for the task runner.
        bower.json: Front-end packages installed by bower.
        package.json: Development packages installed by npm.

        app/: Your application files.



Grunt commands:

grunt serve --target=300x250
grunt build --target=300x250
grunt cdnify
grunt sprite

Bower commands:

bower install packagename --save
bower wiredep


Sub Generator:

yo banner:add [name]